              "free_text": [
                "",
                "By compiler (2017-12-28):",
                " The monitor cross section value is not given in the",
                " article. However some EXFOR 30403 data sets are",
                " renormalized in EXFOR 31316 with a factor of ~1.15,",
                " which could imply that the 56Fe(n,p)56Mn=126 mb at",
                " 14.8 MeV is adopted as monitor value (as it was done",
                " in EXFOR 31247)."
